Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒法突然起跑什麼的… 是有多扯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人的妹妹！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個 我什麼都沒聽到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚什麼的我都沒聽到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說謊爛得嚇死人啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.16,0:02:33.63,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)}#09 真是屈辱、被羞辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:33.63,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)\3c&HF2C855&\bord7}#09 真是屈辱、被羞辱了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在100字以內簡潔回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 100字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 話 還 沒 說 完 呢 給 我 稍 微…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}喂 你都說了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安靜啦！ 我都不知道數到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和小紅可是有婚約的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你給我一邊涼快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 婚約！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶～耶～ 活該吧你～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種事我又不可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}婚約是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 該不會紅緒大人的妹妹也跟我們是同族！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和紅緒大人是同伴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是被奇怪的毒氣污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人跟我們是同族的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒和小紅都不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不是嗎 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那他們倆不是同族卻有婚約了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們也有自己的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有我的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽囑咐過我要是找到同族的男性要馬上佔有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的情況關我啥事～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 那個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未續同學要白夜跟她結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是說未續同學對白夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想你剛剛跌倒要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不要緊啦 不過那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你來這邊沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你們好像在討論有什麼重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是剛剛未續同學說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫你和她結婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「啊」算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我要跟小紅結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是說那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼 你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}婚約的事在學校要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}血痕 沾染著血的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有事件的味道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我才不會被騙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們還提到木葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼什麼啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 該不會是小紅和三峰在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 那你們提到木葉是在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去問本人就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以是怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想他是讓你去問未續同學的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉～ 你在哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺有點受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛剛那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前你說過不要把婚約的事情跟其他人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是自己要他別把婚約的事情說出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被一口否認了卻受打擊什麼的 也太自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說我會受打擊也就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 到底是怎樣啦 那個叫未續的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超失禮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}火大…好火大啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未續同學原本是找真白有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她問我進城是不是因為看中了紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是屈辱 被羞辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被羞辱了是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該不會是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不敢相信 那小不點是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然無法理解紅緒大人有多出色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種人居然還生活在紅緒大人的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到木葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅和三峰提到木葉是在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 提到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是在嘲笑我在走廊大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小不點爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有我不知道他們倆有婚約還去求婚的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 看看紅緒大人的照片
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 我問了小紅和三峰有沒有在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被否認了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他們倆一直都在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還以為這能成為一個不錯的八卦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人妹妹的戀人曝光什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不是有婚約的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 說是說婚約 其實是那種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是很常見的那種父母擅自決定的婚約呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然當事人不願意 那我也還有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}復活！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話題歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到最後還是不明白是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說末續同學喜歡白夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然有了證據照片 說服力就會上一個檔次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.342\fs50\c&H63BAE8&\pos(504,583)\3c&H8157B2&\shad0}頂級機密領域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有點事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 昨天和末續幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因為紅緒 害我受了天大的屈辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要怎麼賠償我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不太明白 但我會負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是無法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼紅緒大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 害羞了 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}於是呢 其實是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次總該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人氣爆棚的姐姐大人總是去找真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以您身邊的人吃醋了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我想您是不是不要總是去找真白比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是竟然為了我引發了紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是悲傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是跟末續關照一聲比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 會把事情搞得更麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概已經沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是末續同學誤會了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為真白一直在躲著姐姐大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎… 呃…咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我和真白碳很要好所以吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}於是難道說 小紅也在吃醋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是的 沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃？ 咦…小紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回來的時候去買雞蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天做戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在網路上有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想嚐嚐那個巧克力戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就做巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一說和姐姐大人一樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然真白可能不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但姐姐也是有很多優點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事都能做到 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人氣很高也是值得高興的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的話可能與其說是吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說是有點寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然還要讓妹妹為她操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說起來 就因為同族很少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就突然要白夜和她結婚 她到底在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經告訴她小紅和白夜有婚約了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告訴她婚約的事了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣我會很頭疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是很好嗎 雙親公認的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正大光明一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是如果傳出八卦我會很頭疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是被大野同學聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可能又會被追著不放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去囑咐她不要外傳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她會乖乖聽話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會放棄是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是說紅緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然末續同學是喜歡白夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擔心婚約的事情會被大肆宣揚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊… 雖然也有這個原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}親自去拜託一下不行的話就談條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}賄賂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}賄賂！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}照片怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個人不是拿著很多紅緒的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不知道用來幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要多給她看看紅緒的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定會醒悟過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺主旨有點偏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去拍就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}潛行可是我的拿手好戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總…總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去拜託她不要把婚約的事情說出去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會的工作請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也一同度過祥和的學園生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒主教…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然真白碳的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是傲嬌沒錯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上說對紅緒大人不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果卻是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然嘴上說了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是經受不起紅緒大人的魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是既然這樣也要給窩有個相應的態度啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在學校裡還真是沒什麼破綻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 這個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我是紅緒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以連我也被討厭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事呀 找我有什麼事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我有何貴幹呀 真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你瞎搞個啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你才搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那個 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因為我大放厥詞說了不會放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}關於和白夜婚約的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒也沒打算去大肆宣揚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是未婚夫你卻跟仁子說沒有和三峰交往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}並且還叫我保守這個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說你不願意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不願意的話 解除婚約如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣對男方也有失禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果婚約解除了 我也就能遵從媽媽的叮囑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能和同族結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛剛那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也知道這樣有失禮數…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是很不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是末續同學的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是我把她弄哭了一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道我要遭難了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的 就是垃圾吹進了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不得了 去保健室嗎 要不去眼科看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們關係很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯呢 畢竟是同屆的 最近經常聊天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嘛 那小紅就承蒙照顧了 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有真白也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她就像是我可愛的妹妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請跟她們好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…那再見啦 末續同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放學後見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼睛進了垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅那可愛的眼睛裡面進了垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼睛進了垃圾…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太誇張了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說校內清掃工作沒有做好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 在今後的每一小時裡設立一次清掃活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我會在會議上提案的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別做那種濫用職權的事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這也是為了學校好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 趁現在拍下她的怪相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要和小紅在一起就經常出現古怪言行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}校內環境整潔也會增加舒適感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}露餡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然真白碳的態度是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人要我和小不點和睦相處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嘛 俗話說越吵架關係越和睦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不和睦呢 我說的不是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和睦相處有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟真白和小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時她為什麼會哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 戚風蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 軟綿綿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請從我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個給真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的照片 看你很想要的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都說了上次不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}簽名… 自己設計的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然哭了出來 給末續同學添麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得去道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對男方也有失禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 想再拿一些棒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說啊 我做了蛋糕要不要嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有做得太甜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種甜度就沒問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 關於婚約的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之所以請你保密是因為怕傳開了被人戲弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃…就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}並不是討厭婚約的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說 小紅是在說她也喜歡白夜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是木訥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請再給我一塊蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}終於到來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嬌羞期！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是這個意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an7\c&H543AD8&}\N恭\N祝 {\c&H000000&}\N嬌\N羞\N期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後呢 要說到是不是好事… 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好哦 是好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像升級了一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}升級？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你個子太大…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}個…個子太大沒看清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你幹什麼啊 紅緒真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先不說這個 馬上就到白色情人節了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是男人大展身手的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情人節那天有收到小紅的巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次就由白夜送禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一口氣拉近兩人的距離吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那一刻我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冰箱裡的牛奶今天過期這件事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是家庭主婦嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那一刻我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳小內內上的貓咪今天變成了兩隻這件事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下集 查了一下嬌羞期這個詞
